      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s still got so much life left in her! It\u2019s been really well-loved and runs like a dream. It's a super reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
