    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this E46-generation M3, a testament to BMW\u2019s high-revving naturally aspirated era. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously maintained to ensure precise valve timing. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential, providing an analog and engaging driving experience. The chassis has been enhanced with a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and rides on a tuned suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in and lateral stability. This example shows honest wear commensurate with a well-loved driver, but remains mechanically robust with a recently refreshed cooling system and upgraded rod bearings for peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
