    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a driver looking for reliability and aesthetic appeal without the showroom price tag. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor rock chips on the front fascia consistent with standard highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. I have maintained a strict service schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. It has been garage-kept and treated with care. If you are looking for a dependable, well-cared-for example that still turns heads, this is the one. Service records are available upon request.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
