    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who needs a dependable set of wheels without any fuss. It runs great and has been well-cared for over the years! I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to get back on the road with someone new. Drop me a message if you want to come check it out\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
