    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-differential for pure analog feedback. The chassis is well-sorted, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure timing precision. Suspension kinematics remain sharp thanks to refreshed polyurethane bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, featuring a recent valve adjustment and a clean oil analysis. This is a mechanically sound, performance-ready icon for the serious purist.",
